g. Jennifer works in Service Design assisting client stakeholders in the co-creation of superior service, uniquely appropriate for the company or association.[/ult_team][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][ult_team img_hover_eft="" team_member_align_style="left" image="id^1208|url^https://cimatri.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Lisa-headshot-June-2017-Square.png|caption^null|alt^Lisa Gillis Chief Learning Officer|title^Lisa Gillis Cimatri Chief Learning Officer|description^null" name="Lisa Gillis" pos_in_org="Chief Learning Officer"]Lisa Gillis is an accomplished senior executive, entrepreneur, board member, and thought leader with more than 20 years of success in the education, e-learning, business and government industries. Her expertise includes capacity building, process management, designing and implementing ground-breaking programs, governance, strategic planning, e-learning, K-12, program evaluation, curriculum development, coaching, succession planning, public relations, and speaking.[/ult_team][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1500348922744{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-color: #f5f5f5 !important;}"][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeIn" width="2/3"][vc_column_text css_animation="fadeInUp"]

